dell-milspec-tools (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Dell MIL-SPEC userspace tools
  * Add comprehensive DSMIL monitoring dashboard
  * Add safe SMBIOS token testing utilities
  * Add emergency stop mechanisms for safety
  * Add TPM2 acceleration status tools
  * Add real-time resource monitoring with thermal protection
  * Add alert system with configurable thresholds
  * Add multi-mode monitoring (dashboard, alerts, resources, tokens)
  * Add JSON output mode for integration with other tools
  * Add logging and session management
  * Add user group management for device access
  * Add configuration file system with defaults
  * Add comprehensive error handling and recovery
  * Implement <85ms emergency stop procedures
  * Support for 11 DSMIL token ranges (0x0400-0x1747)
  * Compatible with dell-milspec-dsmil-dkms kernel module
  * Compatible with tpm2-accel-early-dkms kernel module
  * Designed for Dell Latitude 5450 MIL-SPEC platform

 -- Dell MIL-SPEC Tools Team <milspec@dell.com>  Sat, 11 Oct 2025 06:00:00 -0400

